                ['The MoSCoW method categorises requirements as Must, Should, Could, Won\'t. A project has limited time. Which category should be delivered first to ensure project success?', ['Must Have — critical requirements without which the project fails', 'Should Have — important but not critical requirements', 'Could Have — nice-to-have features', 'All categories should receive equal priority'], 0],
